Software for Little Magic Boxes (stay tuned).

Home http://github.com/networkimprov/elembe

--- Requirements ---

Linux

Node.js http://github.com/ry/node

Node modules:
  node-inotify http://github.com/c4milo/node-inotify
  node-sqlite http://github.com/networkimprov/node-sqlite
  uuidjs http://github.com/weaver/uuidjs
  gm http://github.com/aheckmann/gm
  socket.io-node http://github.com/LearnBoost/Socket.IO-node

Libraries & Tools:
  SQLite http://sqlite.org/
  libuuid 
  Graphicsmagick http://graphicsmagick.org/
  Xdelta3 http://xdelta.org/
  Socket.IO (in elembe/socket.io/) http://github.com/LearnBoost/Socket.IO

Samba file server http://samba.org/
  configure a share [sqltest] path = elembe/sqltest/

On Clients:

Firefox (currently) http://mozilla.org/

AppLaunch Firefox extension https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/240637/

--- Startup ---

$ node autogen.js
$ node elembe.js autogen
$ node elembe.js
Point Firefox to http://yourhost:8000/

